Detailed Description

Linked List module

Represents generic linked list data structure allows to insert, remove and look for items

See also:
Queue.h, SortedList.h
Author:
Denis Itskovich
Date:
1/12/2008

typedef Comparison(* ItemComparator)(const void *pValueLeft, const void *pValueRight, void *pUserArg)

Compares between 2 values

Parameters:
pValueLeft [in] pointer to first item
pValueRight [in] pointer to second item
pUserArg [in] user defined argument
Returns:
value indicates relationship between items

LESS if *pValueLeft < *pValueRight

EQUAL if *pValueLeft == *pValueRight

GREAT if *pValueLeft > *pValueRight
